headline: HONEYWELL TO RELEASE THIRD QUARTER FINANCIAL RESULTS AND HOLD ITS INVESTOR CONFERENCE CALL ON THURSDAY, OCTOBER 23
summary: Honeywell (NASDAQ: HON) will issue its third quarter financial results before the opening of the Nasdaq Stock Market on Thursday, October 23. The company will also hold a conference call at 8:30 a.m. EDT.
